sheet.description:
At 1st level, you have the ability to use something known as "The Force". You use it mainly through abilities called Force Powers. At 1st level you choose 2 Force Powers, gaining more as you level up. Using these Force Powers costs you Force Points (Shortened to FP) (Note, Force Powers that require one Action to activate, count as an Attack Action, meaning, for the price of 1 attack you can use the appropriate Force Ability without enhancing it, in addidion, you may expand one more attack in order to enhance the Force Ability - 1 Attack Action = Base Force Ability - 2 Attack Actions = Enahnced Force Ability ). 

 In addition, the maximum amount you can spend Force Points to enhance the force power is equal to your level (including the base cost).

